http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: Kentucky Core Academic Standards - Arts and Humanities

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The purpose of the Kentucky Core Academic Standards is to outline the minimum content standards required for all students before graduating from Kentucky public high schools. This document specifies the content standards for the required credits for high school graduation and the primary, intermediate and middle level content standards leading up to these requirements.
